title: Hale Dwoskin - Sedona Method Absolute Freedom inc Workbook MP3
description:
Uncover Your Natural State of Being

Easily recognize and dissolve the barriers that you imagine are keeping you from perceiving your true nature. You will discover that who you are has only appeared to be hidden by your self-imposed sense of limitation. You have always been absolutely free.

Absolute Freedom deals with the question Who Am I? by helping you strip away the illusion of problems and circumstances which prevent you from seeing what is. Hale guides the listener through holistic releasing and the subject matter tends to go much deeper. This is where we learn to let go and dissolve the issues that distract and prevent us from realizing our true nature our Presence.

As you apply Holistic Releasing to your life you will find that even long-standing challenges dissolve and are replaced by a greater sense of mastery.

Course Contents

Audio Set 1: Opening to Freedom
Audio Set 2: Beyond the Illusion of Time and Space
Audio Set 3: Opening to Love
Audio Set 4: Beyond Self and Other
Audio Set 5: The Finest Level of Creation
30-page Course Booklet

Bonus Recordings

Bonus 1: Remember Who You Are
Bonus 2: Beyond Everything and Nothing
